            <lg xml:id="TK100">
<l>iṉiya vuḷavāka viṉṉāta kūṟal</l>
<l>kaṉiyiruppak kāykavarn taṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Speaking harsh words when sweet words are at hand</l>
<l>is like taking bitter fruit when there is ripe.</l>
            </lg>
